The paper discusses a method for converting the maximization of multi-step survival probability into a reinforcement learning problem, which is a common topic in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE), robotics (cs.RO), and control systems (cs.SY). Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
